citations:
    citation-agot-bran-iii:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Bran III"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Bran wakes from his coma after dreaming of the three-eyed crow. He names his direwolf Summer. Key vision sequence: Bran dreams of Winterfell, his mother on a ship, Arya and Sansa south, Jon at the Wall, and 'deep into the heart of winter' beyond the Wall. The crow whispers 'Because winter is coming' and 'Now you know why you must live.'"
